"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody. Just want to make a quick video about living food and what we're trying to do with regenerative agriculture out here in Neadville, Texas. We are trying to incorporate living soil to grow living vegetables because this is something that's become something of a problem in our society where our food doesn't have the microbial life that it once did, that the bacteria and the archaea and all the different the the web of life that forms around the food is largely vacant. And this is what happens when you do um chemical conventional agriculture. And this is why we're going back to a more traditional way of creating vegetables, which is regenerative agriculture in a broad sense, but it's basically living soil to create living food. This is something we all need to eat more of. Fermented foods are a great example of this, but also just vegetables from a garden that has earthworms in it is a great example as well. Anyway, just want to make a quick video. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody.\",\n      \"start\": 0.48,\n      \"end\": 1.52,\n      \"duration\": 1.04,\n      \"confidence\": 0.979,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \".\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"end\": 1.52,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\